verbose_text: In order to identify further interactions between SHR specific G-1 and G-2 genes, we applied the IPA path explorer tool, suggested the presence of one gene that assisted in these interactions, and found such a condition when we proposed the Jun proto-oncogene (Jun), which interacts directly with specific target DNA sequences to regulate gene expression.
evidence: interactions between SHR-specific G-1 and G-2 genes
